{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/20260329/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"白石研究所"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"c65c4bce-6a7c-5acf-8d92-843f48e1eb75","excerpt":"…","html":"<h2>概要</h2>\n<p>難易度：★（簡単）</p>\n<p>今日は記事のかさ増しを兼ねて、「目玉焼き」を作っていきます。</p>\n<p><del>いやいや、簡単すぎやろ！！（セルフ突っ込み）</del></p>\n<p>油断して火事にならないようにしましょう。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2>卵を割る</h2>\n<p>卵を割ります。どこか角にぶつけます。</p>\n<p>図のように、<strong>殻にひびが入り、かつ卵白が少しはみ出た状態</strong>が割りやすいです。</p>\n<p>卵白がはみ出てない状態で割ろうとすると高確率で黄身が破裂することに最近気づきました。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/shiraken/static/66097e21ddd3a90a72081bc693b207f7/20337/egg.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 77.84810126582278%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"卵を割る例\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/shiraken/static/66097e21ddd3a90a72081bc693b207f7/f058b/egg.png\"\n        srcset=\"/shiraken/static/66097e21ddd3a90a72081bc693b207f7/c26ae/egg.png 158w,\n/shiraken/static/66097e21ddd3a90a72081bc693b207f7/6bdcf/egg.png 315w,\n/shiraken/static/66097e21ddd3a90a72081bc693b207f7/f058b/egg.png 630w,\n/shiraken/static/66097e21ddd3a90a72081bc693b207f7/40601/egg.png 945w,\n/shiraken/static/66097e21ddd3a90a72081bc693b207f7/78612/egg.png 1260w,\n/shiraken/static/66097e21ddd3a90a72081bc693b207f7/20337/egg.png 3082w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<hr>\n<h2>加熱する</h2>\n<p>お好みに合わせて火加減を調節してください。</p>\n<p>私は卵アレルギーなので、本当は両面焼きたい派ですが…</p>\n<p>今日は見栄えのために片面焼きにしてます。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2>完成</h2>\n<p>できました！良い朝です。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/shiraken/static/0240a1d13b87001f017ad30418c5efcc/08485/result.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"完成\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/shiraken/static/0240a1d13b87001f017ad30418c5efcc/f058b/result.png\"\n        srcset=\"/shiraken/static/0240a1d13b87001f017ad30418c5efcc/c26ae/result.png 158w,\n/shiraken/static/0240a1d13b87001f017ad30418c5efcc/6bdcf/result.png 315w,\n/shiraken/static/0240a1d13b87001f017ad30418c5efcc/f058b/result.png 630w,\n/shiraken/static/0240a1d13b87001f017ad30418c5efcc/40601/result.png 945w,\n/shiraken/static/0240a1d13b87001f017ad30418c5efcc/78612/result.png 1260w,\n/shiraken/static/0240a1d13b87001f017ad30418c5efcc/08485/result.png 2014w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"目玉焼き","date":"March 29, 2026","tags":["定番","卵","朝食"]}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/20260322/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"初投稿"}},"next":null},"pageContext":{"id":"c65c4bce-6a7c-5acf-8d92-843f48e1eb75","previousPostId":"e3530acc-f2d1-5864-b912-554684e4f738","nextPostId":null}},"staticQueryHash